# AI Gleanings Dependencies
# Dependencies for AI tooling and development workflow

# Core tools
brew "git"  # Distributed revision control system - https://git-scm.com
brew "gh"   # GitHub command-line tool - https://cli.github.com/
brew "jq"   # Lightweight and flexible command-line JSON processor - https://jqlang.github.io/jq/

# Agent harnesses
# brew "claude-code"  # Terminal-based AI coding assistant - https://www.anthropic.com/claude-code
# brew "codex"        # OpenAI's coding agent that runs in your terminal - https://github.com/openai/codex

# Development tools
brew "node"     # Open-source, cross-platform JavaScript runtime environment - https://nodejs.org/
brew "python3"  # Interpreted, interactive, object-oriented programming language - https://www.python.org/
